Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:16.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}火燒雲在耳邊囁嚅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}接下來到你了
