Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:27.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}反正也是犧牲品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:31.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我是我的世界的王
