Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:44.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(0,300)}在這過於廣大的世界一隅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:50.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(0,800)}心靈融化掉
